  • Classes in edu.illinois.masalzr2.gui used by edu.illinois.masalzr2.gui 
    Class and Description
    Stamp
    A model class used to define simple graphics options to be applied to JLabel or JButtons, both found in the javax.swing package.

    There are two characteristics that are manipulated by stamps:
    - The JLabel or JButton's border
    - The JLabel's or JButton's text

    The border is defined by an integer value that is a multiple of some combination of the first four prime numbers 2,3,5,7 (1 is not considered a prime).
    TradeManager
    Control class.
